{
  "stem": "21978.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "To do work in hospital and to be driven to hospital by a bus-- by a hospital truck, that was fine because that was mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That's in the religious law.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But to do some to my nails on Saturday, or to go and do something else, no, that wasn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I could not stand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I just-- you know, I was-- I liked him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't love him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I just thought I will, after [INAUDIBLE], nothing will be more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But I didn't want to be alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Well, eventually, I left him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we had a lot of trouble before I got my [INAUDIBLE], because he didn't want me to leave.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Eventually, I got divorced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 18 months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I married in 1950.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was divorced in 1952.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "End of 1950, I married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And '52, beginning, I, I got divorced.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was very glad that I was divorced when I met a tourist from Kenya, whom I saw and fell in love the first moment I saw him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that is my present husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew that we were made for each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knew that life continues.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Life goes on regardless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he brought happiness to my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't marry him in Israel, because there was the question of leaving my sister behind again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I-- he-- he make-- he-- how do you say when you get somebody, ex, ex-- he got me, he got me to Kenya to marry him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I married him in Kenya.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His family was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was one of the fortunate Jews in Europe whose family was saved of Hitler-- from Hitler by giving a chance to got a-- get-- they got a visa to get to Kenya, his sister and his mother and father.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
